<div class="app-card-container">
	<div class="card">
		<h1>About Me</h1>
		<hr>
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-4">

				<%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 250, alt: "Profile Image", class: 'profile-img' %>

				<div class="skills">
					<% @skills.each do |skill| %>
						<div class="skill">
							<h4><%= skill.title %></h4> 
							<div class="progress">
								<div 
									class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
									role="progress"
									aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
									aria-valuemax="100"
									style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
								><div>
									
								</div>
									
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>

					<% end %>
				</div>
			</div>	


			<div class="col-md-8">
				<p>As a junior software developer, I've been exploring the realms of Python and Ruby. These two versatile languages have captured my imagination, and I've dived headfirst into their ecosystems.</p>
				<p>One of my early accomplishments includes creating Telegram bots that automate tasks and provide valuable services. These bots showcase my love for practical applications of programming and how it can enhance everyday life.</p>
				<p>I've also ventured into the world of web scraping using Python, uncovering valuable insights and data from the vast internet. This skill has allowed me to gather and analyze information efficiently, which is crucial in today's data-driven world.</p>
				<p>
					<button 
						class="btn btn-primary" 
						type="button" 
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#jobHistory"
						aria-expended="false"
						aria-controler="jobHistory"
					>

						Job History
					</button>

					<button 
						class="btn btn-primary" 
						type="button" 
						data-toggle="collapse"
						data-target="#education"
						aria-expended="false"
						aria-controler="education"
					>

						Education
					</button>
				</p>

				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
						<div class="card card-block">
							CompMechLab® Ltd, Saint-Petersburg, CAE Engineer January 2018-Present
						</div>
					</div>
				</p>


				<p>
					<div class="collapse" id="education">
						<div class="card card-block">
							Peter the Great St.Petersburg Polytechnic University 2017-2019 
							M.Sс Applied Mechanics (Mechanical Engineering).
						</div>
						<div class="card card-block">
							Peter the Great St.Petersburg Polytechnic University 2013-2017
							B.Sс Applied Mechanics (Mechanical Engineering). Mechanics And Control Processes
							Department
						</div>
					</div>
				</p>

			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>